definition.value: An elemental molecule consisting of two hydrogens joined by a single bond.
A sesquiterpene lactone with formula C15H20O8. It is a neurotoxic natural product found in plants of the family Illiciaceae.
An organophosphate oxoanion resulting from deprotonation of the phosphate and carboxy groups of N-(5-phospho-beta-D-ribosyl)anthranilic acid.
